A layered cake made of translucent blue crystal and glass, floating in mid-air, with one slice being lifted away revealing intricate glowing circuit patterns inside each layer. The cake sits on an ornate silver server hovering above swirling clouds. Multiple delicate glass forks float around it, each fork connected by thin luminous threads to different layers of the cake. The scene is bathed in soft cyan and warm amber light, with a dreamy atmospheric fog. Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures, gentle gradients, and whimsical floating elements that suggest magic and wonder in technology.
